      <title>房主仍留在原地，Trex 押注房屋改造</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-03/trex-bets-on-remodeling-as-homeowners-stay-put-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着夏季气温升高，Trex 的需求也随之飙升。这家户外装饰巨头正加倍投入 DIY 爱好者，押注装修热潮。首席执行官 Brian Fairbanks 在“彭博市场”节目中与彭博社的 Katie Greifeld 讨论了他的前景。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-03/trex-bets-on-remodeling-as-homeowners-stay-put-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 15:38:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着新的指控浮出水面，道明银行贿赂丑闻蔓延至佛罗里达州</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/td-s-bribery-woes-spread-to-florida-as-fresh-allegations-surface</link>
      <description><![CDATA[多伦多道明银行佛罗里达州分行一名长期工作人员收受了数笔 200 美元的贿赂，以帮助客户绕过反洗钱法规将数百万美元转移到哥伦比亚，这一指控进一步加剧了该银行在美国面临的法律问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/td-s-bribery-woes-spread-to-florida-as-fresh-allegations-surface</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 15:33:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约证券交易所故障导致一些股票大幅波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-03/glitch-at-nyse-leads-to-some-wild-stock-swings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约证券交易所运营商出现明显故障，导致包括 Chipotle 和伯克希尔哈撒韦在内的大约十几家公司暂停波动性交易。纽约证券交易所证实，该公司遇到了“技术问题”。彭博社的凯瑟琳·多尔蒂报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-03/glitch-at-nyse-leads-to-some-wild-stock-swings</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 15:18:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市政债券市场面临两年来最大的 190 亿美元供应浪潮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/muni-market-faces-19-billion-supply-wave-biggest-in-two-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年市政债券销售的持续增长没有丝毫放缓的迹象，因为投资者准备迎接两年来最大的新债券发行量增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/muni-market-faces-19-billion-supply-wave-biggest-in-two-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 15:05:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Blackstone 的 Blitzer 委托 Lazard 处理奥格斯堡足球俱乐部的潜在出售事宜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/blackstone-s-blitzer-taps-lazard-for-potential-fc-augsburg-sale</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，德国足球俱乐部奥格斯堡足球俱乐部的一位关键投资者正在试探潜在的出售可能性，该球队的估值可能超过 1.5 亿欧元（1.63 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/blackstone-s-blitzer-taps-lazard-for-potential-fc-augsburg-sale</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约证券交易所故障导致十几只股票停牌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/volatility-halts-hit-numerous-nyse-listed-stocks-in-error</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约证券交易所运营商出现明显故障，导致开盘后不久，包括 Chipotle Mexican Grill Inc. 和雅培实验室 (Abbott Laboratories) 在内的十多家公司的波动性交易暂停。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/volatility-halts-hit-numerous-nyse-listed-stocks-in-error</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 14:08:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>私人信贷，华尔街最热门的交易，正遭遇困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/private-credit-wall-street-s-hottest-trade-has-an-ugly-moment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[多年来，随着私人信贷激增为一个价值 1.7 万亿美元的产业，市场最大参与者的说法是，他们的交易简而言之就是更安全。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/private-credit-wall-street-s-hottest-trade-has-an-ugly-moment</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>葛兰素史克股价暴跌，因制药商必须面对特拉华州的 Zantac 诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/gsk-plunges-as-drugmaker-must-face-zantac-cases-in-delaware</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法院判决英国制药商葛兰素史克公司以及赛诺菲等其他制药商必须接受有关其胃灼热治疗药物 Zantac 是否会导致癌症的审判，随后葛兰素史克公司股价暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/gsk-plunges-as-drugmaker-must-face-zantac-cases-in-delaware</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 07:14:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
